des:
Compete against other players in a match featuring five celebrity voices!

Try and beat your high score on our worldwide leader board!

⭐Yak Yak Games Unlimited⭐

Voice Blast is part of Yak Yak Games, you can subscribe to get unlimited plays in Voice Blast, as well as access to premium features in Deal or No Deal, Yak Yak Quiz, What Came First, The Million Dollar Money Drop, Jeff Stelling's Sports Quiz and Song Blast.

You can link your account in the Amazon Alexa app to get email notifications of new updates and features! 

 To play just say: Alexa, open Voice Blast!
